<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mobile Hour - Customer reviews</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <main>
        <%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>
        <h1>Customer reviews</h1>
        <h2>Our customer says</h2>
        <section class="customer-review">
            <section class="customer-card">
                <figure>
                    <img src="images/customer1.jpg" alt=" customer 1 image">
                    <h2>Janny</h2>
                    <h3>5 of 5</h3>
                    <figcaption>I just bought a new mobile and I am very pleased with this deal.</figcaption>
                </figure>
                <figure>
                    <img src="images/customer2.jpg" alt=" customer 2 image">
                    <h2>John</h2>
                    <h3>5 of 5</h3>
                    <figcaption>Very helpful service and price is good. I like the product so much! </figcaption>
                </figure>
                <figure>
                    <img src="images/customer3.jpg" alt=" customer 3 image">
                    <h2>Jessy</h2>
                    <h3>5 of 5</h3>
                    <figcaption>Website is a really nice and there have many products to choose.</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </section>
        </section>
        <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>
    </main>
    
</body>
</html>

